title: Eric Clapton - Blues(Includes Jams Bonus Duisc)(1999)FLAC-Cue
description:
The Blues is a Blues Rock compilation album by Eric Clapton released in 1999. The release features songs from Clapton's
 1970s RSO albums, as well as some unreleased material from the same era. The second disc features live recordings.
   
===============================================
